content.rendered:
BD Sharps Collector for medical sharps waste. Australian Made to Australian Standards AS4031

One way non-spill opening. Built-in needle notch removal system. Screw top lid. 1.4-litre capacity. Yellow plastic. The container has a maximum fill volume line positioned at the recommended fill capacity.

excerpt.rendered:
General
Medical sharps wasteWarnings
Do not reuse
Do not overfill
